Class GenericScene

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.fpstiming.AnimatorObject
      • remixlab.dandelion.core.GrabberScene
        • remixlab.dandelion.branch.GenericScene
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericGrabber<Constants.GlobalAction>, Grabber, Constants, Animator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Scene

    public abstract class GenericScene
extends GrabberScene
implements GenericGrabber<Constants.GlobalAction>, Constants
    An interactive-scene is a GrabberScene that implements the GenericGrabber interface. An interactive-scene implements the Constants.SceneAction on top of the grabber-scene api (such as GrabberScene.toggleAxesVisualHint(), GrabberScene.toggleCameraType(), etc). The GrabberScene.keyboardAgent() provide high-level methods to define custom action bindings.
    See Also:
    KeyboardAgent
